This default storage contains mani types, messenger, vostan.

For privacy notices, it is strongly recommended not to use the OpenAI API.
For privacy reasons, use of the OpenAI API is strictly not permitted.

Certificates:
	Metax certs you can generate using gen_certs.sh ( FQDN must be localhost ).
	For greenhosting webserver use Let's Encrypt.

Vostan startpage UUIDs:
	Read-only: 
	eff7378c-5c64-4bf8-bc13-a185f649e96e-3005988a-aca6-448e-b26c-66444b4ad17e

	Editable: 
	da774a74-ad61-40e4-96d9-cc18ce20329b-6f0032ed-7c37-4fec-8642-8c6c669bc4ef

Installing node modules:
	cd metax_2
	npm install

	cd greenhosting_webserver_2
	npm install

Changes and updates by CyberHayq:
	1) Greenhosting webserver always using certs from cmdline config (npm start), for prevent server private key leak.
	   Server certificates do not need to be uploaded to metax.
	2) Smart startup and logging system:
		2.1) Metax starting by systemd service.
		2.2) Metax logging by systemd service or bash, with logs rotating.
	3) Automatic sitemap generation.


